These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: horror, animation
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, water-polo
City: hamburg, rome
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person watching animation movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation    | horror |
| Sport         | water-polo | skiing    |
| City     | hamburg     | rome      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
House: cape-cod, palace
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| House      | palace  | cape-cod   |
| Sport   | rugby | badminton  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
House: gothic-revival, colonial
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
City: marseilles, boston
1. the colonial house is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| House         | gothic-revival   | colonial  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| City         | marseilles   | boston |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, raspberry
House: townhouse, futuristic
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, vegafina
1. the prince-smoker is on the right of the futuristic house##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | pomegranate | raspberry |
| House   | futuristic   | townhouse   |
| Cigar     | vegafina       | prince      |

