.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: rock-climbing, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, dancer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, metal
1. the fan of metal is on the left of the accountant##1
2. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Hobby    | drawing | rock-climbing     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Music-Genre   | metal | classical    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-8::.
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, pumpkin
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, october
2 different games are played: backgammon, go
1. the person playing go is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person eating pumpkin is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |
| Food        | pumpkin | blueberry  |
| Birthday       | may | october |
| Game   | backgammon    | go |

