The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, family
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, lizard
1. the owner of the lizard is in an even position##4
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
