.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, badminton
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, indian
City: marseilles, miami
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
2. the colombian is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Sport         | badminton | lacrosse |
| Nationality   | colombian     | indian     |
| City           | miami          | marseilles     |

