.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-20::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, romance
The people have 2 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily
1. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | action | romance |
| Hobby   | gardening  | rock-climbing  |
| Flower     | lily | tulip    |

 